<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="149">Hyphal structure.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="149">Hyphal system monomitic; generative hyphae with clamp connections, smooth, hyaline to pale yellow, CB+, IKI-; tissues becoming dark in KOH.</paragraph>
