<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="149" type="remarks">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="149">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="149">
The buff-yellow pore surface, darkening when touched or bruised, the small pores (6-9 per mm) sometimes with white tomentum, and the ellipsoid small basidiospores (3.1-4.2 
